Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,*Episode 2 – seating change
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,*Take me

Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.68,0:01:05.23,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's true that I was attracted by his kindness,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.23,0:01:11.50,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,his coolness, his honesty, his outgoingness.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.88,0:01:13.70,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.66,0:01:16.76,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,no mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.12,0:01:37.95,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can expect to see you over the summer, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.86,0:02:19.74,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,My name is Kuronuma Sawako.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.72,0:02:24.15,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope someone nice will adopt you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.54,0:02:32.88,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,My nickname is Sadako.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.88,0:02:35.66,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Like Sadako from Ringu.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.84,0:02:40.33,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,My favorite phrase is, “Do one good deed a day.”
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.75,0:02:44.76,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you hear?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.76,0:02:46.38,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sadako from Class B...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.38,0:02:48.35,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That girl who has a psychic aura or whatever?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.35,0:02:49.27,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.27,0:02:53.16,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Before the summer break, she made a public announcement that she got rejected.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.16,0:02:54.53,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.53,0:02:55.61,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By who?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.24,0:02:58.40,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ka-ze-ha-ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.40,0:03:00.28,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kazehaya?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.66,0:03:03.69,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She wouldn't have a chance with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.64,0:03:07.98,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.10,0:03:18.26,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah, it's because I approached them out of nowhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.26,0:03:20.49,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry to scare you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.49,0:03:21.70,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's praying.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.70,0:03:23.51,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is there something there?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.19,0:03:28.27,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if that puppy is okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.80,0:03:30.74,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is she staring into the void?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.74,0:03:33.21,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And why is she soaked?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.27,0:03:39.12,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,It's hard to approach people,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.12,0:03:41.11,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,and I have a hard time talking to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.02,0:03:46.08,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,But I still hope I can break down that wall.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.97,0:03:49.24,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.61,0:03:53.21,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're soaked, Kazehaya.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.76,0:03:54.97,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I got caught in the rain.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.97,0:03:57.71,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, all those people are crowding around him.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.09,0:03:59.71,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,That's Kazehaya-kun for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.38,0:04:02.92,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,He's cool even when he's drenched.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.43,0:04:13.73,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.45,0:04:18.10,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,M-Morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.10,0:04:20.18,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,He still talks to me like normal,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.18,0:04:23.49,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,after all the trouble I've caused him.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.49,0:04:25.45,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,He's so nice!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.91,0:04:27.78,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you get caught in the rain too?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.78,0:04:29.28,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're soaked.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.28,0:04:30.34,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have any spare clothes?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.04,0:04:33.41,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kazehaya's sure being nice to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.06,0:04:35.64,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Spare clothes?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.64,0:04:40.42,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah, I could have worn a jersey if I had one.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.22,0:04:42.47,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have any?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.85,0:04:46.45,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And that ramen–
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.45,0:04:50.04,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yoshida, don't you have a spare jersey?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.04,0:04:51.60,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.06,0:04:54.86,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.86,0:04:57.06,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have any spare clothes, Sadako?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.27,0:05:01.84,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine, whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.76,0:05:04.78,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.22,0:05:07.16,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tada! 
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.16,0:05:09.74,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It smells moldy. Seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.26,0:05:12.58,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah, could you wash it for me while you're at it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.80,0:05:16.75,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.74,0:05:20.92,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're going to need more than a hanky, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.30,0:05:25.80,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I used it too, so it's a bit wet.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.97,0:05:29.80,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tha– Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.03,0:05:34.31,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,It's hard interacting with people,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.30,0:05:40.78,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,but these days I think there are a lot of really nice people.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.63,0:05:43.82,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.82,0:05:46.65,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,My classmates lent me stuff!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.54,0:05:51.30,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to thank them if I can...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.08,0:05:53.16,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Was that a Buddha statue?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.21,0:06:01.34,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it, it was Kazehaya-kun that gave me a chance to befriend Yano-san and Yoshida-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.64,0:06:06.54,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Kazehaya-kun is still my idol.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.54,0:06:08.18,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I admire him.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.87,0:06:12.68,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're worrying too much about her, Kazehaya.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.68,0:06:14.51,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sadako this, Sadako that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.51,0:06:17.71,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know you feel bad about rejecting her, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.71,0:06:18.81,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't reject her.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.45,0:06:22.03,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't accept, did you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.85,0:06:24.70,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not how it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.04,0:06:32.25,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can expect to see you over the summer, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.11,0:06:40.74,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can see you during the summer sessions?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.13,0:06:47.09,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you're not going to avoid me during the sessions?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.55,0:06:49.55,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kuronuma?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.09,0:06:53.81,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've always wanted to be like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.81,0:06:55.68,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've always admired you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.68,0:07:00.69,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I really think highly of you right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.69,0:07:04.90,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think I'll ever stop feeling this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.15,0:07:12.03,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,“Attracted”... she meant that she admires me?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.03,0:07:13.95,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I got so cocky.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.85,0:07:17.62,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, Kazehaya-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.61,0:07:21.96,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kazehaya?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.01,0:07:25.38,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It wasn't about rejecting her...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.78,0:07:27.65,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,or anything like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.65,0:07:30.89,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? I don't get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.89,0:07:33.92,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's me. I was the one who didn't get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.92,0:07:36.39,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I really don't get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.81,0:07:43.48,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,All I ever thought was that I was being a bother.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.66,0:07:51.04,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,But Kazehaya-kun gently let me know otherwise, without faking it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.71,0:07:58.83,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.83,0:08:00.71,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's one on my desk as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.46,0:08:05.54,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sadako left those there.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.54,0:08:07.13,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why me?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.13,0:08:09.42,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's repaying me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.42,0:08:12.13,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're too materialistic.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.07,0:08:19.64,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I never knew happiness could bring tears.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.92,0:08:27.47,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kuronuma!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.47,0:08:30.19,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you give this to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.66,0:08:37.40,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,F-For the towel.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.40,0:08:39.96,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you could have just told me
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.96,0:08:41.37,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,or I would've never found out.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.37,0:08:43.12,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.30,0:08:48.96,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank god it was you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.96,0:08:51.77,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't know what to do if it wasn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.77,0:08:54.93,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I tend to be pretty mindless sometimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.93,0:08:58.47,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought maybe the towel was too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.34,0:09:02.98,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Honestly I'm still a bit nervous.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.15,0:09:05.39,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.15,0:09:10.01,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, didn't Sadako get rejected?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.01,0:09:11.90,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you having milk?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.90,0:09:14.74,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, this is for a dog.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.74,0:09:16.89,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You like dogs?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.89,0:09:19.69,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I saw a dog today, an abandoned one.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.46,0:09:21.75,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Abandoned dog?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.75,0:09:24.00,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I got my clothes wet playing with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.67,0:09:26.85,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,B-By the riverbed?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.71,0:09:35.42,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.61,0:09:41.97,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So this was your umbrella.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.97,0:09:43.94,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why you were drenched.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.94,0:09:45.64,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so embarrassed.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.11,0:09:48.55,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah. It has your name on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.41,0:09:52.53,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been using it since grade school.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.78,0:09:57.03,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can I keep him?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.09,0:09:59.53,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.22,0:10:01.93,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.54,0:10:04.91,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine, I've built up immunity.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.91,0:10:06.51,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Immunity?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.51,0:10:09.52,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Animals have always been afraid of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.52,0:10:11.42,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kids too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.94,0:10:15.42,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I like dogs the most.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.84,0:10:22.18,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah, don't they say dogs get attached to their owner when they're friendly with each other?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.68,0:10:25.61,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See, we're friendly.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.35,0:10:29.19,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Friendly?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.84,0:10:30.23,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.23,0:10:32.69,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.57,0:10:42.32,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,It's strange, whenever he says it, I feel like it's really true.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.42,0:10:46.33,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,This is what he's like all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.49,0:10:51.11,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,He has no prejudice against anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.11,0:10:53.37,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why everyone likes him.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.16,0:10:56.76,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if dogs are the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.76,0:11:02.38,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to break down this thick wall that I have between me and everyone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.38,0:11:04.35,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if just a little at a time.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.98,0:11:06.22,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.33,0:11:11.65,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to be friends with everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.29,0:11:16.71,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.15,0:11:20.15,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, go for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.63,0:11:22.97,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.34,0:11:31.20,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.76,0:11:35.32,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey, if you don't mind...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.83,0:11:39.88,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can I see it again?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.98,0:11:43.89,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What, just the dog?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.89,0:11:44.60,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What about me?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.60,0:11:46.62,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You too, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.62,0:11:48.31,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.32,0:11:52.31,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.28,0:11:56.51,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,It's weird, Kazehaya-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.51,0:12:00.15,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.15,0:12:06.51,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't feel a wall between us.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.08,0:12:12.04,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a first for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.15,0:12:20.37,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe I should wait until after school to give this to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.37,0:12:22.68,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,When there's no one around.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.51,0:12:27.23,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,But I wonder if he'll eat them.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.23,0:12:29.28,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,They're hand-made too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.28,0:12:31.84,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe I overdid it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.94,0:12:38.77,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm breaking out in a cold sweat.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.77,0:12:43.95,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I was used to having this sort of thing rejected.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.95,0:12:45.09,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.45,0:12:48.30,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.92,0:12:51.87,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have math in the first hour, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.33,0:12:53.61,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're in separate classes, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.61,0:12:55.12,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.49,0:12:58.10,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That dog...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.10,0:12:59.50,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's doing well.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.97,0:13:03.17,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I still haven't chosen a name though.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.06,0:13:05.43,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.02,0:13:08.18,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kazehaya.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.13,0:13:11.17,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.72,0:13:23.25,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope he likes the cookies.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.06,0:13:28.03,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, that seat's open.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.03,0:13:30.34,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In the front?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.34,0:13:31.24,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.24,0:13:34.77,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why not? The seat next to it is empty too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.77,0:13:37.20,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's usually here, again?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.20,0:13:38.67,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sadako.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.91,0:13:41.40,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sadako?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.05,0:13:47.86,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuka sat in Sadako's seat and stayed home sick for a week.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.59,0:13:50.76,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.92,0:13:56.45,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.85,0:13:59.49,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.49,0:14:01.38,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not dirty.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.38,0:14:05.49,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing will happen if you sit there.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.49,0:14:09.26,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have the ability to make you sick.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.26,0:14:14.58,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, I don't have any psychic aura or anything either.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.49,0:14:16.71,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I said it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.23,0:14:19.63,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I said it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.04,0:14:28.78,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.41,0:14:33.02,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,There's always next time.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.26,0:14:43.19,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,It won't happen right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.82,0:14:49.94,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll rearrange seating during homeroom. Figure it out amongst yourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.92,0:14:55.60,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't make a racket.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.01,0:14:58.54,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seating change!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.54,0:15:01.82,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei looked pale.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.61,0:15:05.58,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think he's been sick since summer break.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.58,0:15:07.89,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Summer brea–
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.84,0:15:12.97,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it because he made Sadako run more errands?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.42,0:15:16.98,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't Ueda's grades drop? He was beside Sadako.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.98,0:15:19.34,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nakanishi broke a leg.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.34,0:15:23.36,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Remember he said some nasty things to Sadako at the test of courage?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.83,0:15:27.49,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's just do the seating change.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.49,0:15:28.61,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.61,0:15:31.17,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seating change huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.17,0:15:35.95,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope I can become good friends with whoever's next to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.95,0:15:44.67,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it just me or is everyone watching me?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.67,0:15:49.67,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't let me be beside, behind, in front or diagonal to Sadako.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.68,0:15:52.03,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kazehaya, what number?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.03,0:15:53.48,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,32.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.48,0:15:55.46,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're next to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.46,0:15:56.63,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.63,0:15:57.89,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Trade, please?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.41,0:16:01.49,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please? Pretty please?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.24,0:16:03.31,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,He's in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.31,0:16:10.90,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,It sort of sucks that I have no one to share my joy and sadness with at times like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.90,0:16:13.97,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, I'm at the front.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.97,0:16:15.19,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Poor you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.49,0:16:22.81,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.81,0:16:25.45,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm at the back.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.45,0:16:26.63,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you want this?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.63,0:16:28.94,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine, I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.94,0:16:30.51,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.63,0:16:33.23,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sadako's number 3!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.23,0:16:34.68,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's next to her?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.68,0:16:37.29,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,12, 19, 25.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.29,0:16:38.92,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank god, I'm not next to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.92,0:16:40.93,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Number 19 better watch out.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.93,0:16:42.17,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right next to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.58,0:16:47.40,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,That hurts! I heard all of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.73,0:16:52.53,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,But oh well.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.47,0:17:00.04,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I wish I could tell someone that I'm glad I'm here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.15,0:17:04.51,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Number 19, switch with me, please?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.31,0:17:23.52,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yay, I'm next to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.09,0:17:32.79,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can have this back.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.12,0:17:43.97,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yoshida, your draw–
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.97,0:17:45.83,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No thanks, don't need one.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.63,0:17:51.22,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Got a problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.22,0:17:53.13,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuu, move!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.13,0:17:54.07,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Make me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.07,0:17:55.97,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't need to be here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.97,0:17:58.22,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is my seat.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.22,0:18:01.16,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By the window, at the back.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.98,0:18:12.87,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.81,0:18:17.45,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I made cookies to thank you for yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.45,0:18:18.53,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Want some?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.79,0:18:23.20,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For me too?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.20,0:18:23.98,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.98,0:18:26.89,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And the jersey you lent me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.44,0:18:29.79,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's really good.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.94,0:18:33.59,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.24,0:18:36.69,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You baked those?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.69,0:18:38.61,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.61,0:18:41.39,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, that's so thoughtful!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.28,0:18:44.78,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right, they're good.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.85,0:18:47.29,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.16,0:18:50.78,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You just had lunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.81,0:18:53.02,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm hun–
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.63,0:19:10.86,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.82,0:19:13.94,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so glad...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.85,0:19:19.58,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I got this seat.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.96,0:19:23.60,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so happy,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.00,0:19:27.62,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,from the bottom of my heart!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.54,0:19:49.77,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kuronuma.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.85,0:19:55.92,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not crying.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.22,0:19:59.42,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-How embarrassing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.58,0:20:04.11,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Embarrassing, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.18,0:20:08.92,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.92,0:20:12.53,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I work so hard to bring down the wall,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.73,0:20:22.70,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,but he breaks it down with nothing but a smile.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.23,0:20:28.70,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that Kazehaya and Sadako?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.70,0:20:31.72,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't they together a lot lately?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.72,0:20:35.30,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if Sadako really did get rejected.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.34,0:20:40.95,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See you tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.04,0:20:46.09,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I still respect him and admire him.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.91,0:20:49.41,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,That hasn't changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.55,0:20:52.94,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.42,0:21:00.53,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Since when did it become a lot more than that...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.08,0:21:09.83,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,that I started {\i1}really{\i0} liking him?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.94,0:22:27.61,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,New seating arrangements.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.61,0:22:31.20,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My dreams are becoming a reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.99,0:22:35.20,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next episode: After School
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.20,0:22:37.20,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
